import React from 'react'

const ContactForm = () => {
  return (
    <>
    <Formik></Formik>
        <form className='formulario'>   
        <input type="text" className="input_form" id="name" placeholder="Ingrese su nombre" required/>
        <input type="text" className="input_form" id="tittle" placeholder="Ingrese el asunto" required/>
        <input type="email" className="input_form" id="email" placeholder="name@example.com" required/>
        <textarea className="textarea_form" id="message" rows="3" placeholder="Ingrese su mensaje"></textarea>
        <button type="submit" className="btn btn-outline-info btn-lg">Enviar</button>
        </form>
    </>
  )
}

export default ContactForm
